{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Withdraw involvement in war on Iran and seek diplomatic resolution",
        "additional_details": "War with Iran has caused catastrophic humanitarian disaster, regional escalation, and global instability. As a key ally to both US and Israel, UK must use its influence to prevent more civilian deaths, uphold international law, and pursue peaceful solutions rather than military confrontation. The UK must urge comprehensive diplomatic efforts for nuclear non-proliferation and de-escalation throughout the Middle East.",
        "background": "We ask the UK government to publicly declare non-support for any US/Israel military action against Iran. Use diplomatic channels to urge restraint from both governments. Withdraw any military or intelligence support to the conflict and urge peaceful solutions.",
